# TimeCapsuleRevive — PF redirect rules
# Redirect standard SMB ports to Samba's high ports
# AFP and Apple's built-in file sharing remain untouched

rdr pass on bridge0 proto tcp from any to any port 445 -> 127.0.0.1 port 1445
rdr pass on bridge0 proto tcp from any to any port 139 -> 127.0.0.1 port 1139
